sentences:
Empty Estate is an EP by American indie rock act Wild Nothing , released on May 14 , 2013 on Captured Tracks in the US and Bella Union in the UK .
Produced by founding member and primary recording artist Jack Tatum , the EP was released nine months after the band 's second studio album , Nocturne ( 2012 ) .
Regarding the release , Jack Tatum stated : " I feel like I ’ve accomplished in seven songs , on this EP , what I really wanted to do with Nocturne , which is to find a way to compromise all of the things [ I am ] musically .
I think I did that more with this EP than I have everything in the past .
"
